Text: Only 2 singles came out from this album. Why? According to me, this one should have been the third!! Enjoy!

Papa Roach Was A Kick ass Nu-metal Style Band when they came out now there some kind of slow bitch soft rock now . Never the less thanks for the upload ill seed all day.
